 controls are to be changed, and <emphasis>
opts_values</emphasis>
 specifies the new values for those options. The bit values correspond to those
for the <emphasis>
ax_options</emphasis>
 field of an <emphasis>
XkbDescRec</emphasis>
 (see section 10.8). <!-- xref -->
